Module swirlds.platform
Package com.swirlds.platform

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.swirlds.platform.Event
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Event>
    public class Event
extends Object
implements Comparable<Event>
    This is a single hashgraph event. It contains all the info of a hashgraph event, plus some additional info (e.g., its hash). The parts that are a hashgraph event are immutable. The additional (e.g., it's round number) can change.

    This class also includes static constants and methods for handling the transactions that are stored inside the Event.

      • compareTo

        public int compareTo​(Event other)
        Events compare by generation. So sorting is always a topological sort. returns -1 if this.generation is before other.generation, 1 if after, 0 if equal.
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface Comparable<Event>
